channel.title: Froze!
channel.description:
Idk whats going on...everytime i click on the tab to view your bonuses it freezes my client, and doesn't show that menu... i get no errors when i'm in the actual server..
Starting Project X Scape on 0.0.0.0:43594 Made By MsnRocks, Hope You Enjoy! ClientHandler: Accepted from localhost:1245 Client type: low memory version UserId: 56077429 Mod roscoe is signing onto server. Mod roscoe: character file not found. Mod roscoe: moreinfo file not found. LOADED: 3 Game saved for player Mod roscoe ClientHandler: Client Mod roscoe disconnected.
it disconnected because i closed my client... the picture: [URL=http://imageshack.us][IMG]http://img237.imageshack.us/img237/4470/errorcx5.png[/img][/URL] and it just stays there...nothing happens, just frozen forever. I did mess around with BonusName[] and the other stuff around there. but i had a backup and put it in...Still the samething happens, i redownloaded the moparscape client, still same error. i tried another server, pvpScape, and it worked! no freezing...idk did i really mess up my server that much? but i put in my backup and i didn't have that problem before...So anyhelp would really help, like how you bonusName[] looks like. post here! thanks!! alot
